description: The same man with the same clothes, but he has a different beer in his hand. He's standing up and looking at a woman with long black hair, a red dress, and high heels. He's blushing and smiling.
The same man, but his face is not visible because he's kissing the woman.
The same woman, but she's wearing a wedding dress. She's smiling and looking at the camera.
The man and the woman are in a hospital room. The woman is lying in a bed and holding a newborn baby. The man is standing next to her and smiling.
The man is sitting in a rocking chair. He's holding a baby girl in his arms. He's smiling and looking down at her.
